annotationA: CG9865, isoform A; Transferase activity, transferring hexosyl groups. It is involved in the biological process described with: GPI anchor biosynthetic process
annotationB: GPI mannosyltransferase 3; Mannosyltransferase involved in glycosylphosphatidylinositol-anchor biosynthesis. Transfers the third alpha-1,2-mannose to Man2-GlcN-acyl-PI during GPI precursor assembly (By similarity); Belongs to the glycosyltransferase 22 family. PIGB subfamily
